plugin_animator.
Don't forget to edit Makefile to fit your system

The purpose of plugin_animator is to add animation based on
a timeline to crossfire

The differents node in the animation a expressed as a time
in term of crossfire tick or millisecond (at mapmaker choice)

see animfile.txt for specifications of the file

An example of map using it is being created.
If you need it for educational purposes, ask
tchize@mailandnews.com
The animation file used in the map is given in Kronosbad
in this directory as an unfinished  example.

Hope this could be interresting.

Tchize
